STEP 2: READ EACH RANK (from rank 8 to rank 1)
Go through the board systematically. For each rank, list what's on each square (a-h).
Use: K/Q/R/B/N/P for white pieces, k/q/r/b/n/p for black pieces, - for empty.

STEP 3: BUILD THE FEN
Convert each rank to FEN notation:
- Pieces stay as letters
- Consecutive empty squares become a number (e.g., "---" = "3")
- Each rank must total exactly 8 squares

